ign> he <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">is in arrears</tr_> of tax-payments to P. (the tax-collector), <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/78720\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PPetr.\">PPetr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2p.108</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n45656.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐφελκομένοισι πόδεσσιν</foreign> with feet <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">trailing after</tr_> him, of one who is dragged lifeless away, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:696\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.696</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ δ᾽ ἐφέλκετο μείλινον ἔγχος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:597\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.597</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ λίθος ὄπισθε ἐπελκόμενος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dragging behind</tr_> (the boat), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:96\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.96</biblScope> </bibl>; of camels, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:105\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.105</biblScope> </bibl>; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἱ ἐπελκόμενοι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" 